' Global instances
note top right
  **Global Instances (LazyLock)**

  1. PATTERNS: CompiledPatterns
     - Compiled once on first access
     - Used by all handlers
     - Immutable after initialization

  2. COMMAND_CACHE: RwLock<CommandCache>
     - Initially empty
     - Populated on first command lookup
     - Read-heavy workload (99% hits after warmup)

  **Architecture Benefit**
  - Single source of truth
  - No redundant compilations
  - Thread-safe by design
  - Transparent caching
end note

